videos.description:
Today, I, Zhong, take on the wildest challenge yetâ€” If I lose, Iâ€™ll have to shave my head! It all starts with a mischievous 1-year-old who needs a diaper change right away, and things only get crazier from there. The 2 and 3-year-olds cause chaos when Tommy and I try to feed them spaghetti, but they threw it all over the floor. Then comes a 4-year-old who dreams of being a firefighter but is more demanding than we can handle. A 5-year-old throws a tantrum at Walmart, making a huge mess with Doritos, even attacking a store employee! Tommy leaves with the slurpee. iShowSpeed helps me take on a 6-year-old Messi fan who challenges Ronaldoâ€”and we surprise him by bringing Ronaldo to meet him! The 7 and 8-year-olds are evil scientists who almost destroy my house because they dont like Mentos and Coke experiments. Things get worse with a spoiled 9-year-old who makes fun of me for not having as many subscribers as MrBeast and even tries to steal my cats. We gave her a pink McDonald's cheeseburger, but she wasnâ€™t having it. Then, the 10-year-old we picked up from prison wreaks havoc by attacking Spider-Man and Mr Beast, spray painting my basement, and raiding my fridge. Thankfully, my Mas+ was safe, but he stole all my feastables! At least I won in Fortnite. Next, a 11-year-old challenges me for $1,000, and after losing to him in a Fruit by the Foot candy race, Iâ€™m broke! A 12-year-old evil clown throws a pie in my dadâ€™s face, pushes me into the pool, and returns to the circus. The 13-year-old destroys my gaming setup and refuses to play with my claw machine or even the world's cutest cat. Then, a 14-year-old hacks my YouTube channel and forces me to take him on a $10,000 shopping spree for a Nintendo Switch, PS5, iPad, and Roblox Robux at Target. Finally, the 15-year-old bully is the toughest test yet, and I have to build a secret room just to escape him! Who do you think is better, Messi or Ronaldo? Comment below!!

videos.title: Man Builds Hidden UNDER-ROCK Home in the Forest | Start to Finish by @Outdoor_builder
videos.description:
Deep in the heart of the forest, one man takes on the ultimate challenge: building a cabin like something out of a fairy tale entirely by hand. 

Using ancient techniques and natural materials, he transforms raw logs, stone, and moss into a cozy woodland retreat tucked under a towering rock formation. Watch as the walls come alive with hand-cut log rounds, reinforced with traditional mud mortar. Witness the craftsmanship behind the rustic wooden doors, the charming arched bridge, and the organic outdoor rest area.

This is no ordinary cabin, it's a masterpiece inspired by the folklore and fairy-tale charm of woodland homes, blending engineering precision with the enchanting beauty of nature. From the handcrafted windows to the final touches of moss decoration, every step is a journey back to the roots of traditional building. Discover the magic of combining functional design with a storybook aesthetic, and see how this cabin becomes a living testament to ingenuity, self-sufficiency, and the timeless allure of life in the wild. 

Donâ€™t miss this captivating transformation: itâ€™s straight out of a dream!

Guddi Episode 105 - [Eng Sub] - Bakhtawar Rasheed - Kamran Jeelani - Maham Aamir - 7th April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Guddi is a young girl who lives a happy life with her parents. Unbeknownst to them, she can see premonitions. However, her ability soon turns into a nightmare when she foresees her parents' death, and it tragically comes true.

After losing them, Guddi finds shelter with her uncle and aunt, but they oppress her. In her toughest moments, she prays for help and receives it most unexpectedlyâ€”from a doll, the last gift her parents gave her. As the doll assists Guddi through her toughest times, others begin to
learn of its power.

Can Guddi ever find happiness again? Will the injustice she faces finally end? And will people exploit her premonitions and the dollâ€™s power?
